            <title>[LU-3454] open (O_TRUNC) and truncate(0) on a released file must not trig a restore </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3454</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;HSM restore is triggered on data access, to avoid useless restore, it is better to remove released state at open(O_TRUNC) or truncate(0).&lt;br/&gt;
